name: Open Agenda
tagline: A minimalist agenda written in Java.
body:
open-agenda =========== A minimalist agenda written in Java. ![Screenshot](https://raw.github.com/danbraik/open-agenda/master/screenshot.jpg) Create jar file & run with
$ java7 -jar open-agenda.jar
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
